name: FOLD - Yellow Canary
description:
This handmade fold over clutch is perfect for all season. It's ultra chic and it has plenty of room to hold your phone, wallet, make up and more. This clutch begs you to hold them 24/7!

The soft buttery snakeskin finish and the trendy bright yellow color will make you love this bag even more. The simple design makes it a versatile bag for an evening ball or a regular night out with friends. 

-Material: Genuine Python Snakeskin (Outer), Suede Lining (Inner)
-Construction: handmade, hand painted
-Color: Bright Yellow Color
-Finish: Matte, Soft Buttery
-Dimensions: 
10" x 10.5" when lay flat
6.5 " x 10.5" when fold over

This clutch comes with:
- Magnetic snap closure
- Each bag will be sent with a felt dust cover

*If you have any questions, feel free to email me.

name: WEAVE LIMITED EDITION - Atomic Orange
description:

Made from a hand weaved and hand painted python snakeskin, this clutch is a real eye catcher. The rich details, beautiful pop colors and amazing soft buttery snakeskin finish will make you fall in love with this bag even more.

The contrast between orange and black makes this clutch ultra edgy chic and sophisticated as well. The simple design makes it a versatile bag for an evening ball or a regular night out with friends.
